{"tid":2190391,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲要大遊行？乞求中共 有五大訴求？","createTime":"2020-09-05T15:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T11:06:02.000Z","uid":222190,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"837f5d3966a4581f61b289dd9a11cb4c675233aa","tid":2190391,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">預計聽日 ：</span></strong><br />\n警狗set晒陣 &gt; 未開始行 狗已經ss咬人<br />\n&gt; 手足退到商場 &gt; 開始大圍捕 &gt; <br />\n癲狗症發作(例如推跌大肚婆/扑爆頭) &gt; 手足可能轉場 癲狗症再發作&gt; be water 散場<br />\n<br />\n事後大家都好嬲post Ig FB LIHKG <br />\n外國戰線就Twitter, Reddit <br />\n<br />\n之後警謊 港共出黎9 up<br />\n大家再ig fb, 有人就寫篇野 抽下警謊水咁<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>以上事件無限輪迴</strong></span></p><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n上年 全靠手足犧牲, 街頭抗爭<br />\n令到美帝作出制裁行動<br />\n宜家有足夠子彈(中共警暴, DQ議員, 手足受不合理對待）<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">但制裁成效 未如香港人所想</span><br />\n<span class=\"red\">香港最勇武時期</span>已經過去<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">抗爭熱潮不再 連聯署簽名都唔夠人</span><br />\n好多人連Twitter 都冇<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\">點解宜家仲要 大遊行？</span></p></span><br />\n乞求中共 有五大訴求？<br />\n儲子彈比美帝？話比人知 抗爭冇靜過？<br />\n想學白俄 烏克蘭咁勇武？<br />\n香港咁多黃絲 有幾多人肯罷工罷稅 大家一齊衝？唔通你覺得 黃碧雲會一齊衝？<br />\n每次想勇武 就同對家講埋 日期時間地點<br />\n過左成年 除左食黃店抗爭 仲可能點樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通大家可以 <span class=\"gold\">韜光養晦 強身健體買裝<br />\n         We will be back?</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nBtw我都係打篇野放灰 做垃圾失敗撚<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"> 最緊要 聽日大家萬事小心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a694a504bdb50d4aa8fcf4e48cd520da431bdd","tid":2190391,"uid":222190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUyrfOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUyrfOv.png&h=ff8a2ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=8e1bfdff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"5a132959661a56eca66ff7afd2a895eb396f5fc1","tid":2190391,"uid":222190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:20:12.000Z","msg":"就算大家唔shopping<br />\n都希望幫手簽下聯署 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6905a2753098ff485fbdb7142f55746f59f6894","tid":2190391,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"差一萬 推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64e27c27e676a06135f06300ae5f7f1b66af508","tid":2190391,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6905a2753098ff485fbdb7142f55746f59f6894","tid":2190391,"uid":179825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"差一萬 推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b2e57cc866bf00a73a924f62bd1028f0608e47","tid":2190391,"uid":179825,"like":